description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gaston purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 310, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60625-66170-1.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [310 Votes, Hall of Fame]
